title: IndyCar Series - 2014 GoPro Grand Prix of Sonoma 720p [PT-BR | E
description:
With a brief delay I could finally provide the IndyCar Series's Sonoma Race, this time on a road circuit which is very difficult to overtake containing lot of selective corners. Brazilian commentaries by Nivaldo Prieto and Felipe Giaffone on audio track 1 while English commentaries by NBC SC team crew on audio track 2. 

ATTENTION: English audio track starts at 2min15s
ATTENTION 2: Brazilian feed suddenly interrupted the broadcasting during an analysis of the incident at the end of the race by NBC commentaries crew. 

At last, sorry for taking so long to provide this. I had an incident with the recording file. In result, i had to record the race all over again on a rerun, which consumed me more time. At least you can download this now before Fontana Race, the final round of Indycar Series.
